item.title: CVE-2023-3118|2023-07-10T13:05:47.247Z -- unknown -- export%20all%20urls
item.description: The Export All URLs WordPress plugin before 4.6 does not sanitise and escape a parameter before outputting them back in the page, leading to a Reflected Cross-Site Scripting which could be used against high privilege users such as admin
